<h1><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>About <%= application.name %></h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>About <%= application.name %></li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<div style="display:none; margin:20px; text-align:center">
		<img width="150" src="images/logos/zigzag.svg" />
	</div>

	<p>SoftServer is a self-hostable cloud based code editor and code sharing platform. It allows you to easily upload, manage, and share your code. Use the public cloud version or host your own SoftServer on your own server! </p>

	<div class="attention"><div class="emphasis">Your Code, <br />Your Server!</div></div>

	<div class="details section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Features</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Self-hostable. </li>
					<li>Easy and intuitive user interface. </li>
					<li>Supports dozens of the most popular languages. </li>
					<li>Share code by link, email, or shared folder. </li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-star"></i>Benefits</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Manage your code using your own server. </li>
					<li>Share code with friends and colleagues. </li>
					<li>Control access to your code. </li>
					<li>Back up your code. </li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<h2><i class="fa fa-desktop"></i>Screen Shots</h2>

	<div class="figure">
		<a href="images/info/desktop/desktop.png" target="_blank" class="smooth lightbox" title="<%= application.name %> Desktop"><img src="images/info/desktop/desktop.png" /></a>
		<div class="caption"><%= application.name %> Desktop</div>
	</div>

	<div class="figure row">
		<div class="figure col-sm-6">
			<a href="images/info/desktop/iphone-desktop.png" target="_blank" class="smooth lightbox" title="<%= application.name %> Mobile"><img src="images/info/desktop/iphone-desktop.png" style="width:300px" /></a>
			<div class="caption"><%= application.name %> Mobile</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>